articles.title: Miss America 2025: Miss Alabama Abbie Stockard wins the crown - AL.com
articles.description: Abbie Stockard, from Birmingham, is the fourth Miss Alabama to win the title of Miss America. She's a student at Auburn University.
articles.content:
Abbie Stockard, Miss Alabama 2024, was crowned Miss America 2025 on Sunday night at the Walt Disney Theater in Orlando, Florida.
